Land & Home Deals
Choose Your Land ‚Äî Or Build in Our Featured Subdivision

At Gulf South Homes, we make it easy to build your future with a complete land and home package. Whether you already found your own land, need help locating a property, or want to build in one of our featured communities, we handle the entire process from start to finish.

You can choose any land you find, and we can include the cost of that land directly in your loan.
Or, you can choose a lot in our featured subdivision, La Belle Maison, with new phases available.

La Belle Maison Subdivision

Located conveniently in southeast Louisiana, La Belle Maison is a growing neighborhood developed in partnership with DR Development Group, LLC.
It offers:
Available lots ready now
