Permits
We Handle Every Permit Your Home Needs ‚Äî Completely Turnkey

Permits can feel overwhelming, especially when every parish has different requirements. Gulf South Homes makes it simple by handling every permit and inspection for you from start to finish.

You don‚Äôt deal with paperwork.
You don‚Äôt call the parish.
You don‚Äôt track approvals.
We take care of everything.

Everything in One Place (Turnkey Service)

We handle the entire permitting process on your behalf ‚Äî so you never have to figure out who to call or what forms to fill out.

We handle everything from going to the Board of Health to get your sewer permit, to applying for your building permit, to scheduling all final inspections ‚Äî all turnkey, so you don‚Äôt have to.

Permits We Take Care Of

Depending on your parish, your home may require:
Sewer / Board of Health permit
Building permit
Setup permit
Electrical permit
Plumbing permit
Mechanical / HVAC permit
Driveway or culvert permits
Elevation or floodplain compliance

Whatever your parish requires ‚Äî we handle it.

No Headaches. No Guesswork.

You don‚Äôt have to:
Contact the Board of Health
Figure out which permits apply to you
Call the parish office
Complete forms
Track inspection dates

Our team manages the entire process for you, ensuring everything is submitted, approved, and ready before your home arrives.

Compliance Made Easy

We make sure your home meets all local requirements, passes inspections, and stays on schedule ‚Äî giving you a truly turnkey experience.


